CRMD THE FDA Meeting is very close On Monday it will be 4 weeks from this statement Now that the FDA has granted our meeting request we are in the process of preparing the meeting material for submission to the FDA The procedures for the FDAs Center for Drug Evaluation and Research or CDER require that when the request for a meeting has been granted a background package of all of the material for discussion with the FDA be prepared and submitted We are in the process of assembling the background package based on the analyses that have been conducted since the data in the locked database became available and our interpretation of those results Meeting material must be submitted to the agency as defined by the FDAs requirements
